Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:04.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Outou Festival" "Seeking possible \Nplans for opening ceremony acts"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Arts Festival... it's \Nalready that season.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exams are coming up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second trimester is always a pain \Nbecause there's so much stuff to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything else you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the final Arts Festival of your \Nhigh school career looms before you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening Ceremony? What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Outou Festival, each year, there \Nis a tradition to gather volunteers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have them perform something \Nas the opening act.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought of something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:38.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"To Be Decided"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we've decided on \Na fortune-telling house,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so before the next homeroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please think of what kind of \Nfortunes you will be telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tooth-brushing exercises - 7" "History of paulownia \Narmoires and how to make them - 1" "Haunted house - 6"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did your best! I'm touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'm thinking about \Ndoing a cheerleading dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:00:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Opening Ceremony \Nmentioned this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best performance \Nto liven up a festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... It'd sure be flashy, \Nand it sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it? We are going to \Ndominate the talk of the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, we're already included in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that I had to have the \Nplans down to a certain extent,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including who was going to participate...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-{\i1}chan {\i0}might not be able \Nto make it, stamina-wise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not troubling anyone, \NI'd like to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble? Of course you wouldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's going to be a big project,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I might be slowing everyone down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is something that I \Nwant to challenge myself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Even Yutaka's going that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if everyone else is doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have made such wonderful friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Fortunes, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can you tell fortunes at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, how bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you came up with the idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunes that you tell in an arts \Nfestival can be really random.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what is your class doing, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're doing standard \Nfare, a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so pedestrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't come up with any \Nother interesting ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just thinking how perfect that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you implying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a real-life demon has gotten angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Patty-{\i1}chan {\i0}said that she \Nwants to do a cheerleading routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I thought I'd do \Nmy best for a bit, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! But why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been absent from school so much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I've never really done \Nanything with everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, I've been feeling a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought, what I've always been wanting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what Patty-{\i1}chan {\i0}is wanting right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are probably the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still think it would be rather tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, because we definitely \Ndon't have enough people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty-{\i1}chan {\i0}wanted to know if \Nyou would participate too, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how you're doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you're good at athletic stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if people like you and \NMinami-{\i1}chan {\i0}are with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can try my best until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to go that far, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if Patty is saying so too, \Nthen you've got a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Patty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard about it, and \Nwas wondering what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ding ding ding ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a certain ticket \Nin my hand right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what is this a ticket for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata, you were really \Ninto Gekisou, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to have a passionate \Nhandshake with Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A handshake party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go! I want to go! Aya in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Konata, were \Nyou saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have to do our \Nbest making memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, you two, the current \Ngeneration is about cheerleading.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of reason is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty started talking about \Ndoing a cheerleading routine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the opening ceremony \Nof the Arts Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yeah, she'd look good in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was decided that you two will \Nbe dancing too, Tsukasa, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are there any other people in \Nyour class that can join in, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take the ball and run \Nwith it without telling us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can do anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you won't get a \Nchance like this ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the opportunity of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all doing this amongst \Nfriends, and it's a festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it would be "the more the merrier," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, you're easy to convince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against it. I have to make \Npreparations for our class, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sob, sob...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that it would be nice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make memories with everyone \Nin our final Arts Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quick to talk about \N"friendship" all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's so obvious you're acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-{\i1}chan {\i0}is really gung-ho about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her that she'd be \Nbetter off passing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's really giving her \Nall about doing something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,together with everyone else right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're having problems \Nwith getting enough people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was why they're asking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I may have been a \Nbit too forceful about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't force you into it, \Nso I'll try asking other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My class can find a replacement \Nfor me in their act,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't find one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you really are cute after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Cheerleading?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I can pull that off well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, right now, I'm feeling \Na bit unsure myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...especially in volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well-endowed"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could be a part of it, I \Nthink it will turn out really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. If I can be of any help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you, well-end... er, Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exams are over,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're going to start seriously \Npreparing for the Arts Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But make sure you don't loosen up too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there are a lot of events going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be nice to ease up \Non the number of exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata, what's going \Non with the cheerleading?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard "the plans went \Nthrough!" Before the exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't heard from her since.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be in trouble \Nif we don't get practicing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we might already be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I haven't done the \Nchoreography or anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't made it? What \Nare we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it took time to find an \Nappropriate song and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't quite get something \Nlike {\i1}Hare-Hare {\i0}going...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, if you were worried about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could have tried consulting \Nthe other people in the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You organized it, so take responsibility \Nfor doing the schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand difficult Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! \NYou're totally fluent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, at least figure out \Nsome of the choreography!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can fix the rough parts \Non the fly as we practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get it, ask \Nsomeone you can chat with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki and I will deal \Nwith the basic schedules
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and securing a location to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagamin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so reluctant about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you know, you seem to be the \Nmost passionate about it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use tarot cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Actually, I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, is there something \Nthat even I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about telling fortunes \Nbased on the shape of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shape will most likely show
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:09:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your romantic fortune is on the up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, you just thought \Nup that one, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second... We're going \Nto try that, starting today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that it's bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it will be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to drop the difficulty level
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the really hard parts \Nas we practice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, how bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a huge wave of awe will be \Nwaiting when we overcome them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to hear that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of masking tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I guess we'll go buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you get markers too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And replacement blades for the cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And cardboard boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And an issue of Playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something weird in that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like, if there are \Nthat many things to buy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,quit fooling around and someone \Nhurry up and go buy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were we calling the yakisoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was "Spring's Fragrant Breath."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was "Fallen Drop of Sun's Dew"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an okonomiyaki pancake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to figure out the menu \Njust by hearing what they're called.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese culture is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it can be overdone too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z... 'Zuka cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"1-D Outou Festival exhibit" \N"'Zuka cafe 'Class: Wind'"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cafe where you enjoy \Nsimple shows done 'Zuka style.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pick a girl in a glamorous dress
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or a noble cross-dressed \Ngirl as your waitress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross-dressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Yu-{\i1}chan {\i0}and Minami-{\i1}chan \N{\i0}will be our top servers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unfolding kaleidoscope of beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did we decide all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about the cheering \Ntoo, but will this be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:56.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful! Now, let's \Ntry it again from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. They're perfectly \Nin sync with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Miyuki-{\i1}san {\i0}being sadistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it Minami-{\i1}chan {\i0}being masochistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True... the dynamic dancing of Takara-{\i1}senpai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may prove to put pressure on Minami-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, you two. Go practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cheerleader costumes are done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is wonderful, but it \Nis slightly embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That type of costume is the kind \Nthat makes the audience happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this outfit was chosen by someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's really happy to see \Ngirls in these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've heard stories about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The formidable elder brother \Nof the Tamura family...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can look forward to \Nthe 'Zuka costumes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Yutaka, you guys \Nare doing a cheerleading routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I record it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we haven't gotten \Na single successful run,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's pretty much on the brink of failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some of my sisterly \Npower, so you go do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to accept your power, Sis,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd get needlessly energetic, \Nonly making me more tired in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we don't have much time \Nleft, but we have so much to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The arts festival, huh... What \Ndid we do when we had one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to do something like what \Nyou'd call a manga cafe nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boys in our class would \Nall bring their own manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys were ahead of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays it's normal to bring \Nstuff like that to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but back in our day it was rather strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only during festivals \Nthat we could do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are people that bring them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not exactly allowed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so a fortune-telling house, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell everyone to give me \Ngood fortunes if I show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That would defeat the \Npurpose of fortunes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, back in your day, Mother, \Nwhat were the arts festivals like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each class and each club \Nput on various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What everyone did were the typical things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like haunted houses and okonomiyaki shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange to think that things were \Nbasically the same then as now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, were there \Nany exhibits on cultural items,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such as paulownia armoires?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about? Doing something \Nlike that wouldn't be any fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can put on an \Nenthusiastic performance somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like it's perfect yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so let's stay focused and \Nkeep going till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, it's really \Nhelpful for Hiiragi to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because she keeps us going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't like to be the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't have any memories with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Grin, grin, grin, grin"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! Don't look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"16th Outou Festival" "Now \Nis the time to glimmer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so? I'm \Nterribly sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently today is a day just for students,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which doubles as a rehearsal for all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we ordinary folk can't \Nenter until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said to make sure \Neverything was okay before we came!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I heard that Akira-{\i1}chan \N{\i0}was going to be here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was a waste of the train fare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had that money back, I'd \Nbe able to buy hamburgers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have lived a slightly luxurious life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this sense of incompletion \Nis really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it. Hey, are you actually \Nwandering around in that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better this way. I \Nmean, it's advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s costume is really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to start with appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell a lot of fortunes today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will buy a soft-serve 5 \Nminutes and 15 seconds from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drop it 5 minutes and 28 seconds from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fortune-telling... \NThat's more like a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hit your head against a sign 7 \Nminutes and 6 seconds from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're copying it word-for-word!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you are wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're not going to lose either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just in the nick of \Ntime, but they're finally done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are very wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really embarrassing to \Nwalk around in this outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, but it's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, it's almost time for \NAkira Kogami's stage performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! I'll be right over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, ma'am. I'm Akira Kogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to do my best today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Sakuraba. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is something like a rehearsal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so feel free to relax and just \Ncheck things out. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiraishi! I'm leaving \Nit to you to do the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shiraishi, chairman of the Arts \NFestival Operations Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll basically be leaving \Nthe rest to Shiraishi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so if you have anything, tell him. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, why don't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be going to the monsters' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a little carried \Naway planning things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}, you are a valued guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I will escort you accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this, we'll have you do a mike test
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for {\i1}Cape Thirties {\i0}({\i1}Misoji \NMisaki{\i0}) In {\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I'll have you do a \Nfree-talking panel afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll make sure to do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please head to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that cheeky Shiraishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you for \Ncoming here just for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you have lots of fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will I finally arrive in the arms
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the person I care for so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A solitary journey, wandering \Nand roaming about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,carrying with me the words from that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:15.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The 16th Annual Outou Festival"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as you can go, searching \Nfor his semblance in shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have her sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Akira Kogami, with {\i1}Cape \NThirties {\i0}({\i1}Misoji Misaki{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Alone... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, let me sing properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that it was a test, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:32.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't understand \Nsuch difficult Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all of you ready? This \Nis the last run-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was an idea that came \Noff the top of my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I'm really happy that \NI was blessed with this chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to do something with all of you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not worry about success or failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just get out there and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The ambiguous 3cm? Does that \Nmean it's plushy? Wait! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The wrapping is a uniform, \Nargh, it's not an act, pooh ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Gotta do your best, gotta just do it ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ That's time to catch 'n' release, eek ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Between sweat (whoop) Sweat (whoop) ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Darlin', darlin', freeze! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Kinda lethargic, something's \Nkinda comin' out ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I love you... Oh wait, one \Nof those was different ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Worrywarts, high metal bars ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Tasty thoughts... And that's enough! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The heated body of that \Nflying you-know-who ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It's what you call a normal girlie ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Surprised? I'm the only \None who got seconds ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ On pork-bone broth ramen \Nwith wire-hard noodles ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Da da da da da ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Pom-poms cheer squad ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Let's get cherry pie ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Happy fun welcoming party ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Look up! Sensation ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yeah! Feeling of existence, \Ndot dot small planet ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Collided and it melted \Naway, in total awe ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Go all out to sing, shi-ranger! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Take it away! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I should be the one who'll \Nbe laughing in the end ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:19:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Because I have the sailor suit \N← This is my conclusion ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It's only Monday! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Already in a bad mood? What to do? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I really prefer the summer outfits \N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3 ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Until we approach 3 pixels, \Nno hesitations please ★ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Do your best, be energetic ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ My darlin', darlin' please! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, how bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you guys were still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were practicing the cheerleading routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And how is that going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's something to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, we're thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can at least treat girls \Ndoing their best to a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's fine. A special \Ntreat, today being what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in return, for tomorrow's \Nfestival opening,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get them all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Actually, I'm \Nfeeling a little lonely myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the most fun time of a festival
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is when you're getting ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Tomorrow is the real deal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have any more occasions \Nwhere we stay at school this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think of it that way, \Nit really gets a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamura-{\i1}san{\i0}, your face is all tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, my stomach hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, you're tense all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but you don't look \Nas confident right now yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The more nervous I am, \Nthe more focused I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm so nervous that \NI can't move anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Testing, testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, from this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're declaring the Outou \NFestival to be open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first exhibit was planned by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our overseas studies student, Patricia-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cheerleading squad made up \Nof a group of really good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and give them a big welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:32.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Min min miracle Minorun-run! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me, there's a cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's my phone! Oh, no... Whoaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble up to the very, very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt so much power draining from \Nme that I thought I'd fall over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it, like, really uncool?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say trouble is always \Npart of the deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could say that this \Nis what you can expect from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sense of non-closure is definitely that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez, I'm really sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get back in gear, \Nand have them perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song is {\i1}Take it Away! Sailor \NSuit {\i0}({\i1}Motteke! Sailor Fuku{\i0})!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Your whims have started \Nto move once again ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It's so sad, this means it's the end ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I'm sure you're having \Ndreams of that girl again ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ With a sigh, I say \Nso long to my dream ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ She's an angel, no, she's a devil ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Ah, to you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ She's the person that \Nsets a sweet trap ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Your love is paradise ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:22:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Repeated only to disappear ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The "I love you" inside your lips ♪
